| Component | Detail |
|-----------|--------|
| Host OS | Ubuntu Server 24.04 LTS |
| Host IP | 10.200.200.253/24 |
| Gateway | 10.200.200.254 (OPNsense) |
| Deployment Method | Docker Compose |
| Docker Version | 26.x |

## Architecture

All services run as Docker containers on a single dedicated VM, connected via an internal Docker bridge network (SOC_NET). This isolates inter-service communication from the host network while exposing only the required ports externally.

```
Ubuntu SOC Server (10.200.200.253)
│
Docker Engine
│
SOC_NET (bridge network)
├── TheHive       → port 9000
├── Cortex        → port 9001
├── MinIO         → port 9002 (console)
├── Elasticsearch → port 9200
├── Cassandra     → port 9042
├── MISP          → port 80 / 443
├── MISP MySQL    → internal only
├── Redis         → internal only
└── MISP Modules  → internal only
```

